ng Systems , 2018, pp. 4480––4490. [8] Akash Chintha, Bao Thai, Saniat Javid Sohrawardi, Kartavya Bhatt, Andrea Hickerson, Matthew Wright, and Raymond Ptucha, “Recurrent convolutional structures for audio spoof and video deepfake detection,” IEEE Journal of Selected Topics in Signal Processing , vol. 14, no. 5, pp. 1024–1037, 2020. [9] Shruti Agarwal, Hany Farid, Ohad Fried, and Manee", "stderr": "", "interrupted": false, "isImage": false, "noOutputExpected": false}}
